{"tid":1453183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭：等我哋一齊以愛國愛黨的心，祈求用警棍、子彈、仇恨引領香港再創高峰","createTime":"2019-08-12T03:29:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T03:37:15.000Z","uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"345df57c655db95f0cbf3153cb1de2dabd95b99c","tid":1453183,"uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:29:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hOQAFLt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhOQAFLt.jpg&h=43c7a98b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在剛過去的星期日，她出席聖公會舉辦的「燃亮香港」崇拜，禮儀由鄺保羅大主教主持。六大宗教均有派代表出席，而代表天主教的是陳副主教。林鄭表示：「一如往常，我今朝返聖母聖衣堂參加周日彌撒；到下晝，我到聖約翰座堂參加『燃亮香港』感恩崇拜，慶祝香港多年來喺各方面取得嘅成就。<span style=\"color: red;\">等我哋一齊以愛國愛黨的心，祈求用警棍、子彈、仇恨引領香港再創高峰。</span>」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1050608\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1050608&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpM%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=653a88dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1050608&h=bfdbe5a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1050608</a>"},{"pid":"b1f11370a6c67f8685aae20b633be66f2b962762","tid":1453183,"uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:31:16.000Z","msg":"777: Burn Hong Kong!!"},{"pid":"f8a3a7780a73c7a1b0215865a89291fcd19ff14c","tid":1453183,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:31:31.000Z","msg":"原話<br />\n林鄭表示：「一如往常，我今朝返聖母聖衣堂參加周日彌撒；到下晝，我到聖約翰座堂參加『燃亮香港』感恩崇拜，慶祝香港多年來喺各方面取得嘅成就。等我哋一齊以謙卑的心，祈求信、望、愛引領香港再創高峰。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e544bc9ea7c7b5d711de117f196eebbd94107b00","tid":1453183,"uid":31320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f8a3a7780a73c7a1b0215865a89291fcd19ff14c","tid":1453183,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:31:31.000Z","msg":"原話<br />\n林鄭表示：「一如往常，我今朝返聖母聖衣堂參加周日彌撒；到下晝，我到聖約翰座堂參加『燃亮香港』感恩崇拜，慶祝香港多年來喺各方面取得嘅成就。等我哋一齊以謙卑的心，祈求信、望、愛引領香港再創高峰。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:32:04.000Z","msg":"信、望、愛？<br />\n有咩?"},{"pid":"627b2470411d63db990439a2873b9dd254f003c6","tid":1453183,"uid":301523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:32:27.000Z","msg":"2017年<br />\n<br />\n勿推"},{"pid":"c5f72a44c0cf685db2d2fa0daa761e59af748ba4","tid":1453183,"uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"627b2470411d63db990439a2873b9dd254f003c6","tid":1453183,"uid":301523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:32:27.000Z","msg":"2017年<br />\n<br />\n勿推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:33:32.000Z","msg":"偽善天主教徒，點解唔推?"},{"pid":"c09dfdaffac61ffdb32d73f6b8c6bd2aba8c4795","tid":1453183,"uid":259141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:36:01.000Z","msg":"地獄等緊妳一家四口, 仆街"},{"pid":"d5ee749cdd37bf5ad1d0fa4f01f9131b14fd782e","tid":1453183,"uid":20379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:36:46.000Z","msg":"左邊個個撚樣唔係死左喇咩<br />\n回魂呀?"},{"pid":"79bb20f3bdffee524d90527b25d6f684bbd1bede","tid":1453183,"uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5ee749cdd37bf5ad1d0fa4f01f9131b14fd782e","tid":1453183,"uid":20379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:36:46.000Z","msg":"左邊個個撚樣唔係死左喇咩<br />\n回魂呀?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}